  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899040/extras/a02db74b02273195225b0fdca5b3be2f.poster.avif?t=1715727245\" width=605 height=49 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899040/extras/a02db74b02273195225b0fdca5b3be2f.webm?t=1715727245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Walk a lonely path in Midnight Lane, a chilling horror experience. You play as a young woman forced to navigate a desolate route home after a late shift. The journey takes you through two eerily quiet cities and a subway system that feels more like a descent into something sinister.<br><br>Desolation and Dread:  The environments in Midnight Lane are meticulously crafted to evoke a suffocating sense of isolation. Explore empty streets, abandoned buildings, and dimly lit subway stations, all rendered in a hauntingly beautiful way.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899040/extras/d277ff25f5665a7b9bc582432c5edbf2.poster.avif?t=1715727245\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899040/extras/d277ff25f5665a7b9bc582432c5edbf2.webm?t=1715727245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899040/extras/d277ff25f5665a7b9bc582432c5edbf2.mp4?t=1715727245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The Unknown Lurks:  The game relies heavily on psychological horror, leaving you constantly on edge.  Strange occurrences and unsettling details pepper the journey, keeping you guessing about the true nature of the threat.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899040/extras/16ca9d99d2591d23aaf95a24549a3dd8.poster.avif?t=1715727245\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899040/extras/16ca9d99d2591d23aaf95a24549a3dd8.webm?t=1715727245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899040/extras/16ca9d99d2591d23aaf95a24549a3dd8.mp4?t=1715727245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Inspired by Japanese Horror: The art direction takes cues from iconic Japanese horror movies, setting a unique visual and thematic tone.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899040/extras/a02db74b02273195225b0fdca5b3be2f.poster.avif?t=1715727245\" width=605 height=49 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899040/extras/a02db74b02273195225b0fdca5b3be2f.webm?t=1715727245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Walk a lonely path in Midnight Lane, a chilling horror experience. You play as a young woman forced to navigate a desolate route home after a late shift. The journey takes you through two eerily quiet cities and a subway system that feels more like a descent into something sinister.<br><br>Desolation and Dread:  The environments in Midnight Lane are meticulously crafted to evoke a suffocating sense of isolation. Explore empty streets, abandoned buildings, and dimly lit subway stations, all rendered in a hauntingly beautiful way.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899040/extras/d277ff25f5665a7b9bc582432c5edbf2.poster.avif?t=1715727245\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899040/extras/d277ff25f5665a7b9bc582432c5edbf2.webm?t=1715727245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899040/extras/d277ff25f5665a7b9bc582432c5edbf2.mp4?t=1715727245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The Unknown Lurks:  The game relies heavily on psychological horror, leaving you constantly on edge.  Strange occurrences and unsettling details pepper the journey, keeping you guessing about the true nature of the threat.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899040/extras/16ca9d99d2591d23aaf95a24549a3dd8.poster.avif?t=1715727245\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899040/extras/16ca9d99d2591d23aaf95a24549a3dd8.webm?t=1715727245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899040/extras/16ca9d99d2591d23aaf95a24549a3dd8.mp4?t=1715727245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Inspired by Japanese Horror: The art direction takes cues from iconic Japanese horror movies, setting a unique visual and thematic tone.",
